01:18:54.772 --> 01:18:56.898
-Do you need a hand with that?
-l got a full house.

01:18:56.982 --> 01:18:59.567
-l got you beat. l got the straight flush.
-Full house, he's got.

01:18:59.652 --> 01:19:03.029
